{
  "files": [
    {
      "repo": "sg-evals/expressjs-express",
      "path": "package.json",
      "version": "0.7.1"
    }
  ],
  "text": "The security audit of the Node.js web stack repositories identified one package.json file that declares 'cookie' as a direct runtime dependency: sg-evals/expressjs-express/package.json, which specifies version 0.7.1. This version is not vulnerable to CVE-2024-47764 as it is >= 0.7.0, but it is the only direct runtime dependency on the 'cookie' package found across the audited repositories (nodejs/node, expressjs/express, lodash, and prisma-prisma). The other repositories do not have 'cookie' listed under their runtime dependencies - they either have no dependencies section at all (lodash, prisma-prisma) or no reference to 'cookie' (nodejs/node)."
}

